text.tspan: Comedy and Tragedy are extremely dramatic little
masks who really like to escalate situations. They
also enjoy imitating people: Today I saw them with a
suit on that is just like yours! Quite dapper. They also
enjoy possessing people, but there aren't very many
people for them to possess nowadays. I think it might
just be you and me. So don't be alone in a room with
them; they will make you do some embarassing stuff
if they get their hands on you. The one time I have
been possessed by them, they made me make popcorn
and try to give it to Abby (she's a ghost and can't eat).
She promptly began to cry, because she thought I was
acting not like myself. So just stay away from these
assholes.
Comedy & Tragedy
The imitators
Age: 210
Species: Magic items
Alignment: Neutral/Chaotic
Alternative subtitle:
Glorified flashlight
